{"tid":1770094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廁所協會：政府翻新公廁進度緩慢衛生情況惡劣","createTime":"2019-12-05T08:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T08:37:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"be232c5775993ab1be7e766d4890621ac0ed9af1","tid":1770094,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"有機構巡查全港過百間公廁，發現政府翻新進度緩慢，衛生情況惡劣，又提倡加裝女性尿兜，改善女廁大排長龍的問題。<br />\n<br />\n香港廁所協會就過去一年全港公廁情況發表報告，巡查全港約160間公廁，發現深水埗區北河街街市公廁衛生情況最差，政府翻新進度亦不理想。<br />\n<br />\n協會又認為，本港男女廁比例1:1.5，造成女廁經常大排長龍，提議加建女性尿兜，配合即棄尿斗輔助。<br />\n<br />\n女性尿兜的空間只佔普通廁格的一半，成本與一個洗手盤相若。普遍女性都習慣入廁格坐低如廁，協會建議尿兜旁可以加裝浴簾及圍板，提高私隱度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2oMrf0y9k6tgq3kcEPuWLw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/TOILET-AWARD-191205-1415.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2oMrf0y9k6tgq3kcEPuWLw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FTOILET-AWARD-191205-1415.jpg&h=0f20c06f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BB%81%E6%89%80%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%BF%BB%E6%96%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%BB%81%E9%80%B2%E5%BA%A6%E7%B7%A9%E6%85%A2%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E6%83%A1%E5%8A%A3-063034464.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25BB%2581%25E6%2589%2580%25E5%258D%2594%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25BB%2581%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E6%2585%25A2%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581%25E6%2583%25A1%25E5%258A%25A3-063034464.html&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=2bc1d15e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BB%81%E6%89%80%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%BF%BB%E6%96%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%BB%81%E9%80%B2%E5%BA%A6%E7%B7%A9%E6%85%A2%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E6%83%A1%E5%8A%A3-063034464.html</a>"},{"pid":"c07a8150e6a993e3a4263688243c9c75de3f2b25","tid":1770094,"uid":272321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T08:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢次冇得反對&hellip;"}]}